metadata.name: Choice
metadata.description:
Where does the search begin? 
How do we define who we are and who we want to become? 

Choice 

Everyone has to decide, listen, feel - take the first step - make a choice.
We acknowledge ourselves when we follow our choices. When out of a thousand seemingly completely different, but very similar in essence solutions, we choose what is closer to our spirit. 

We acknowledge ourselves when we follow our choices. When we move towards that which is closest to the natural nature of our spirit.
